high_descs: Turn around and head to the counter left of the sink.
Pick up the tomato on the counter.
Turn around and bring the tomato to the microwave.
Heat the tomato in the microwave.
Bring the tomato to the left side of the microwave.
Put the tomato down on the table in front of the microwave, to the left.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated tomato on the table next to the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around, then turn left, then turn right to face the counter to the left of the sink.
Pick up the tomato from the counter.
Turn right, go straight, then turn right again to go to the microwave.
Cook the tomato inside of the microwave.
Turn left, move forward, then turn right to face the microwave again.
Place the tomato at the left front corner of the counter with the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked tomato on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and face the counter to the left of the sink.
Pick the tomato up from the counter.
Go right and then turn and stand in front of the microwave on the black stand.
Put the tomato in the microwave, start the microwave, take the tomato out and shut the door.
Move to the left and stand in front of the counter to the left of the microwave.
Set the tomato down on the left edge of the counter top.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated tomato on the counter.
